    <string-array name="grounding_steps">
        <item>Look around. Name five things you can see — anything at all.</item>
        <item>Notice four things you can feel. Your feet on the floor. Fabric. Air.</item>
        <item>Listen. Find three sounds, near or far.</item>
        <item>Two things you can smell — or two smells you like.</item>
        <item>One thing you can taste. Take a slow breath.</item>
        <item>You\'re here. The wave is already passing.</item>
    </string-array>
    <string-array name="muscle_steps">
        <item>Sit or stand comfortably. Take one slow breath.</item>
        <item>Make fists. Squeeze for five seconds — then let go completely.</item>
        <item>Shrug your shoulders up to your ears. Hold… and drop them.</item>
        <item>Scrunch your face gently. Hold… and soften everything.</item>
        <item>Tense your stomach. Hold… release, and breathe out long.</item>
        <item>Press your feet into the floor. Hold… and let your legs go heavy.</item>
        <item>Scan head to toe. Wherever you find tension, breathe into it and let it drop.</item>
    </string-array>

